{"id":"sinite","term":"Sinite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>An inhabitant of Sin, near Arka (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 10:17\">Gen. 10:17</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 1:15\">1 Chr. 1:15</a>). (See ARKITE.)</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 10:17","1 Chronicles 1:15"]}